title: Custom profiles default credPath to directory; forever Not logged in
updated_at: "2026-07-15T05:57:19Z"
---
## Problem
Custom profiles require `entry.path` and `entry.provider`, but `credPath` defaults to `entry.path`. Placeholder examples use a config directory path (`/home/me/.claude-custom`) without `credPath` or provider-specific auth filename, so `cat` runs on a directory and the profile forever shows “Not logged in.”

## Location
contents/ui/ProfileController.qml:219-230

## Suggested fix
Resolve auth file from provider when `credPath` omitted (e.g. claude → `path/.credentials.json`, codex/grok → `path/auth.json`, minimax → `path/config.json`). Document and validate in KCM.

